     <l n="2" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">She reproach'd   with Neglect or with Malice,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">That the Slattern had left, in the Hurry and Hast,</l>
